From a118b2c65826be5740655202dab67d8821c4635f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sri Vidya Gunturi <sgunturi@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 30 Apr 2025 10:20:07 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 08/20] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL: hostapd: Add support for EPCS WMM
 and MU EDCA elements

Modify the existing APIs - hostapd_eid_he_mu_edca_parameter_set and
hostapd_eid_wmm to get the MU_EDCA element and WMM elements for the EPCS
params.

The frame format for these elements is based on the section -
9.4.2.322.6 EPCS Priority Access Multi-Link element, from the
IEEE P802.11be/D7.0 Specification.

Signed-off-by: Sri Vidya Gunturi <sgunturi@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 src/ap/beacon.c        |  8 ++++----
 src/ap/ieee802_11.c    | 10 +++++-----
 src/ap/ieee802_11.h    |  3 ++-
 src/ap/ieee802_11_he.c | 23 +++++++++++++++++++----
 src/ap/wmm.c           | 14 +++++++++++---
 src/ap/wmm.h           |  2 +-
 6 files changed, 42 insertions(+), 18 deletions(-)

--- a/src/ap/beacon.c
+++ b/src/ap/beacon.c
